{"tid":1737772,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【母子平安】46歲蔡少芬第3度當媽 終於追到個仔可以收爐","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T13:09:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"375cc98541d6aeca5fa5e3ca8b15f7e53de1843d","tid":1737772,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"恭喜！46歲蔡少芬（Ada）第三度做媽媽，終於追到個仔，上周五誕下麟兒，老公張晉今日在微博開心留言：「11月15日，母子平安，歡迎來到張家，我們平安回家啦！」<br />\nAda和老公張晉結婚11年，育有一對女兒，曾公開自爆10年拍攝《後宮甄嬛傳》時小產，多年來努力追仔，可惜一直未能成功，本來打算放棄生仔念頭，怎知上天給她夫婦二人意外驚喜，今次真的可以正式「收爐」了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191119/large/1574137576_e600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574137576_e600.jpg&h=362c60c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191119/60284235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284235&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=c8c06ced\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284235&h=306c3cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191119/60284235</a>"},{"pid":"19c6bc0ac7a732c27638984e9f2744d3bd7e2b26","tid":1737772,"uid":213193,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"好羨慕"},{"pid":"6a479ac65350ffeda2a5a7f439feb4b767436483","tid":1737772,"uid":27027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"唔推文"},{"pid":"eeafecfba7579e28385417ca4de3474efb9f0ae4","tid":1737772,"uid":249761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"Ada嫁得真係好"},{"pid":"d21339d94b705939de0ce0c13e6d7081e226e398","tid":1737772,"